Still have the original parts. Aftermarket trigger for a lighter pull. Rotating red dot mount that allows the sub2k to still be closed. Recoil buffer pad. Single point sling mount. Cheek pad.  -Less than 1k rounds fired with no jams. -White spray coating applied for “Storm Trooper” look . Can be removed with an acetone, or pain thinner. Originally a dark green. -exceptional quality, but I recently got a 9mm AR that is replacing it though.
